                        <interp inst="t18400615-name-648" type="given" value="JEREMIAH"></interp>JEREMIAH CAMPBELL.</persName>
                  </hi>I am a pawnbroker, and live in High-street, Newington-butts—I received this portfolio in pawn of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner pleaded poverty.)</p>
